response.original_title: Dueto Voces del Rancho: Pura Raza
response.overview: The Mexican band Dueto Voces del Rancho -- a duo composed of Edgar Rodriguez and Mariano Fernandez -- perform a blend of traditional favorites in this collection of live performances that also features Mexican singer Lupillo Rivera.
